      "content": "i know they love me, but love doesn't fix the exhaustion they feel. they're sacrificing everything for me. if i were gone, they could finally breathe and focus on their own families and careers. it feels like i'm just holding them back from being happy. wouldn't it be a kinder thing to just let them go? to just stop being the problem?",
